(44, 1, 1, 43, 18, 19, 21, 'all that Jesus began both to do and teach', 'Teaching and Public Discourse', 'This connection highlights the theme of Jesus'' public teaching. Both passages emphasize Jesus'' openness in sharing his doctrine, as seen in ''all that Jesus began both to do and teach'' and ''I ever taught in the synagogue''.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
